com.axelor.studio.service

Class ModelImporterService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axelor.studio.service.ModelImporterService

  • public class ModelImporterService
extends java.lang.Object
    Service class import Models from excel file (xlsx). One excel sheet represent one model. It will create MetaModel, MetaField, ViewEditor and MenuEditor from sheet data. Excel sheet must be in predefine format to be able to import. Also process is all or none , so if any single error occur it will abort importing. It process MetaMenu to create model and MetaField to create field xml.
    Author:
    axelor

      • updateMinMax

        private void updateMinMax(MetaField field,

        Special method to update min and max property for field types, string,decimal and integer. String and Integer type of field share same integer min/max property.
        Parameters:
        field - MetaField to update.
        row - Excel sheet row containing data.
        decimal - Boolean to check if to process decimal min/max or integer min/max.

      • updateFieldTypeName

        private MetaField updateFieldTypeName(java.lang.String fieldType,
                            MetaField field,
                            org.apache.poi.ss.usermodel.Row row)
        Method set 'typeName' of MetaField, it convert simple type names used in sheet into ADK supported type Names. Like it convert 'int' to 'Integer' and 'char' to 'String'.
        Parameters:
        fieldType - Simple field type.
        field - MetaField to update.
        row - Excel sheet row to find reference model in case of relational field.
        Returns:
        Updated MetaField.
